headline: YOUR HAPPY PLACE HAS ARRIVED - CELEBRITY XCEL OFFICIALLY SETS SAIL
summary: The happy place of vacationers has officially arrived. Celebrity Xcel has arrived in Fort Lauderdale, Florida, introducing seven brand-new experiences designed to offer guests endless possibilities on their dream vacation. headline: Royal Caribbean bets big on destination strategy
summary: Royal Caribbean's Perfect Day at CocoCay has long been its highest-rated destination by passengers. To build on that, the cruise line is building more Perfect Days, essentially beach and pool resorts that are included with your cruise, and Beach Clubs, similar destinations which will cost extra. ...
